# Home Lab Infrastructure

## Devices
- ARC-LAP-01: Arch Laptop (Gateway + Zabbix Server)
- PRX-SRV-02: Proxmox Node 1 (VM host)
- SW-MDM-03: Nokia Modem (Dumb Switch)

## Network Layout
- Subnet: 192.168.1.0/24
- Gateway: 192.168.1.105
- Pi-hole DNS: 192.168.1.150 / 1.1.1.1

## Virtual Machines
- Ubuntu VM: Zabbix Agent
- Pi-hole VM: DNS filtering
- LXC container: Snipe-IT (planned)

## Key Configurations
- IPv4 forwarding and NAT on Arch laptop
- Tailscale VPN optional
- Monitoring via Zabbix
